{"tid":136476,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 也傻眼了？iPhone 7 Plus 送修後隔天爆炸！","createTime":"2017-02-27T05:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T02:18:35.000Z","uid":2339,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e303c58f1d32599eec80264e394c719713bdfcf6","tid":136476,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/28921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F28921&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6VKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=685aa56e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F28921&h=30e921b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/28921</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2017/02/25/170225-28921-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2F170225-28921-1.jpg&h=7ba2962e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／Phone Arena）<br />\n<br />\n在 2016 下半年手機電池爆炸大量出現，讓消費者對於於手機的電池安全加倍重視。然而似乎再怎麼小心，也無法防範爆炸意外的發生。這次的事件是一名 iPhone 7 Plus 用戶，當他把故障手機送去維修後，隔天手機就自己爆炸了！<br />\n<br />\n根據《Phone Arena》的報導，iPhone 7 Plus 用戶 Brianna Olivas，由於先前遇到 iPhone 7 Plus 無法開機的問題，因此將手機送到原購買處 Sprint 電信門市進行檢測。<br />\n<br />\n該門市檢測人員指出，這台 iPhone 7 Plus 雖然有些奇怪，但檢測結果顯示手機沒有異常。結果隔天 Brianna 的男友透過 Apple 原廠充電器替手機充電時，iPhone 7 Plus 就開始冒出白煙，接著就開始爆炸。<br />\n<br />\nApple 已經連繫該用戶，並且提供更換的手機。針對這個爆炸事件，Apple 僅提到已經展開調查，由於是使用 Apple 原廠的充電方案，因此 Apple 恐怕得在花上數週的才能找出手機爆炸的原因。<br />\n<br />\n完整 iPhone 7 爆炸影片在此<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/briannaolivas_/status/834556234166448128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbriannaolivas_%2Fstatus%2F834556234166448128&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6VKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=f8346b50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbriannaolivas_%2Fstatus%2F834556234166448128&h=765780dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/briannaolivas_/status/834556234166448128</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4eab48c5f154a6a00154f12e2699280ae2fdb83","tid":136476,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22a2e73f79938e8321ab85d59943c77baf79025","tid":136476,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪高登嗰個香江？"},{"pid":"2bd6b71d92d9b965c781055a816c82257c0cb730","tid":136476,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪高登嗰個香江？</blockquote><br />\n肯定啦"},{"pid":"d67628a4a1b2ef9ed2740ce5d421a6ed6f202fdf","tid":136476,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"死蝗蟲<br />\n傻你老母眼"},{"pid":"95526e5ba6de826588f64b8451b99c92638b1cf8","tid":136476,"uid":13305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T08:00:42.000Z","msg":"傻乜撚眼 大陸西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f71c9ad481748c54b3a55586aa054cb3498ff7","tid":136476,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T08:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪高登嗰個香江？</blockquote><br />\n肯定啦</blockquote><br />\n高登嗰個香江19係咁唱衰LIHKG<br />\n話咩咩小學雞5p至會上<br />\n講到LIHKG咁差自己轉過頭咪又係上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a69c61